{"title":"日常の笔记","date":"2024-01-08T00:08:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 8, 2024","L":"01/08/2024","MM-DD":"01-08"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.cco.moe/pixiv/86770232_p0.webp","link":"post/note","comments":true,"tags":["diary"],"categories":["note"],"updated":"2024-05-10T08:34:47.761Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>日常记录防止遗忘的小笔记，就当个备份～</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"去掉系统更新小红点\">去掉系统更新小红点<a title=\"#去掉系统更新小红点\" href=\"#去掉系统更新小红点\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">defaults write com.apple.systempreferences AttentionPrefBundleIDs 0 &amp;&amp; killall Dock</span><br><span class=\"line\">defaults delete com.apple.systempreferences AttentionPrefBundleIDs</span><br><span class=\"line\">defaults delete com.apple.systempreferences DidShowPrefBundleIDs</span><br><span class=\"line\">killall Dock</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"中国银行借记卡进度查询\">中国银行借记卡进度查询<a title=\"#中国银行借记卡进度查询\" href=\"#中国银行借记卡进度查询\"></a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://cloud.bankofchina.com/sh/html/h5/card/search.html?index=0&amp;apply=direct&amp;parameter=\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.bankofchina.com/sh/html/h5/card/search.html?index=0&amp;apply=direct&amp;parameter=</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"pip安装包的时候指定不使用缓存\">pip安装包的时候指定不使用缓存<a title=\"#pip安装包的时候指定不使用缓存\" href=\"#pip安装包的时候指定不使用缓存\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip install --no-cache-dir nodule_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"pip清理缓存命令\">pip清理缓存命令<a title=\"#pip清理缓存命令\" href=\"#pip清理缓存命令\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip cache purge</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">rm</span> -rf <span class=\"variable\">$HOME</span>/.cache/pip</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">rm</span> -rf ~/Library/Caches/pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\".vimrc开头配置\">.vimrc开头配置<a title=\"#.vimrc开头配置\" href=\"#.vimrc开头配置\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot; Configuration file for vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">set modelines=0\t\t&quot; CVE-2007-2438</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; Normally we use vim-extensions. If you want true vi-compatibility</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; remove change the following statements</span><br><span class=\"line\">set nocompatible\t&quot; Use Vim defaults instead of 100% vi compatibility</span><br><span class=\"line\">set backspace=2\t\t&quot; more powerful backspacing</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; Don&#x27;t write backup file if vim is being called by &quot;crontab -e&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">au BufWrite /private/tmp/crontab.* set nowritebackup nobackup</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; Don&#x27;t write backup file if vim is being called by &quot;chpass&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">au BufWrite /private/etc/pw.* set nowritebackup nobackup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"homebrew中-permission-denied-@-apply2files-解决办法\">Homebrew中 Permission denied @ apply2files 解决办法<a title=\"#homebrew中-permission-denied-@-apply2files-解决办法\" href=\"#homebrew中-permission-denied-@-apply2files-解决办法\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">chown</span> -R $(<span class=\"built_in\">whoami</span>) /opt/homebrew/*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"pip更新包\">pip更新包<a title=\"#pip更新包\" href=\"#pip更新包\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip list --outdated</span><br><span class=\"line\">pip install --upgrade &lt;包的名字&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">pip install -U &lt;包的名字&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>Python更新pip命令如下：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class=\"line\">python -m pip install -U pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"npm换淘宝源\">npm换淘宝源<a title=\"#npm换淘宝源\" href=\"#npm换淘宝源\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或者使用nrm</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install -g nrm</span><br><span class=\"line\">nrm use taobao</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"pip换清华源\">pip换清华源<a title=\"#pip换清华源\" href=\"#pip换清华源\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class=\"line\">pip config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple  <span class=\"comment\"># 永久换源</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip install -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple some-package  <span class=\"comment\"># 临时换源</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"flarum论坛，解决duo-mysql问题\">flarum论坛，解决duo-mysql问题<a title=\"#flarum论坛，解决duo-mysql问题\" href=\"#flarum论坛，解决duo-mysql问题\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get --purge remove php-common</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install php-common php-mysql php-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"剪辑思维","link":"post/jianjisiwei"},"next":{"title":"前期准备-Web前端","link":"post/webpre"},"plink":"http://example.com/post/note/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Charles","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"January 8, 2024"},"reading_time":"392 words in 3 min"}